me.taylorkelly.mywarp.util

Class MyWarpLogger

  • java.lang.Object
    • me.taylorkelly.mywarp.util.MyWarpLogger
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.slf4j.Logger

    public class MyWarpLogger
extends java.lang.Object
implements org.slf4j.Logger
    A custom logger that actually delegates all input to an underlying Logger, but adds the prefix [MyWarp] before each messages.
